snippet.title: Ninkyo Dantai 2023 Progress Update - New Props in GameMaker Studio 3D | Update v1.0.2 #7
snippet.description:
Welcome to episode 7 of the ongoing development of Ninkyo Dantai.

A bit of a different video format today.

In this video, I showcase the new props that TeamCS1 has made, since the start of this year, let us know what you'd like to see!

Huge shout out to Jordan .B the Senior Props Artist.
